    <maintenance>
      <description>        <para>This dataset is typically updated annually, following the completion of the LTER research season and austral summer.</para>
        <para></para>
        <para>Version 9 includes the following updates:</para>
        <para>- New averages up to June 2023 were added.</para>
        <para>- New variables were added: Sum Precipitation, Mean SST, and Mean Windspeed.</para>
        <para>- Previously, “Trace" measurements in the daily data were considered as non-measurements (i.e. NaN).  In this update, they are now considered more properly as 0’s.  Thus, the monthly precipitation counts have increased and the resulting precipitation averages have decreased a bit.  (This only affects older data that had Trace values.)</para>
        <para>- Several daily gaps between 2016-2019 were filled in, which resulted in slight changes to monthly averages.</para>
</description>
      <maintenanceUpdateFrequency>annually</maintenanceUpdateFrequency>
